    "description": "<strong><i>Tunnels under Yorion</i></strong> is a classic roguelike that rewards exploration and player skill during short runs (sometimes just 20 minutes). Fight monsters using turn-based hack-and-slash combat, explore procedurally-generated dungeons, and manage your inventory of weapons and magic items. Make friends and enemies among the denizens of the depths of prison dungeons, catacomb-like caves, and thorny forest.<br><br>In adventure mode, you can make camp in a grotto that has trapped some rich soil. Plant the seeds you found along the way. Grow the plants that might save you on your next run.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165750/extras/ba6f91686167cb5cc6fc4f2d6f395d29.poster.avif?t=1678738769\" width=800 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165750/extras/ba6f91686167cb5cc6fc4f2d6f395d29.webm?t=1678738769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165750/extras/ba6f91686167cb5cc6fc4f2d6f395d29.mp4?t=1678738769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>\tIntuitive combat mechanics<br></li><li>\tProcedural dungeon generation in three unique biomes<br></li><li>\tVaried monster behaviour, leading to complex interactions<br></li><li>\tA variety of consumable fruits and vegetables<br></li><li>\tYour own cavern to plant the seeds you find, and watch them grow<br></li><li>\tRich pixel artwork<br></li><li>\tHit points and experience points, but also status effects like hunger, poison, and curses</li></ul><br>Be sure to ask for help along the way.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165750/extras/a49bd1bd3048d201431c40659067c3ad.poster.avif?t=1678738769\" width=800 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165750/extras/a49bd1bd3048d201431c40659067c3ad.webm?t=1678738769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165750/extras/a49bd1bd3048d201431c40659067c3ad.mp4?t=1678738769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>And keep exploring, you might find new lands as you climb higher.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165750/extras/2189c65e3b8318cdbd0ef134af93611d.poster.avif?t=1678738769\" width=800 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165750/extras/2189c65e3b8318cdbd0ef134af93611d.webm?t=1678738769\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165750/extras/2189c65e3b8318cdbd0ef134af93611d.mp4?t=1678738769\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
